<div class="calcpad-output">
 <!-- Section properties of a right triangle: area, centroid offsets, $I_x$, $I_y$, section moduli and radii of gyration in closed form. -->
 <h3>Geometrical Properties of Right Triangle</h3>
 <div style="max-width:120mm">
  <img alt="right-triangle.png" class="side" src="Images/mechanics/sections/right-triangle.png" style="height:127pt;"/>
 </div>
 <p>Side lengths</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>a</var>
   =
