    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    2 · 1
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   = 1
  </span>
  m
  <sup>2</sup>
 </p>
 <p>Perimeter</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
